Installation
------------

1. Checkout the sources:

   $ git clone https://github.com/marazmiki/osqa-ng.git QA
   $ cd QA

2. Install virtualenv

    $ virtualenv .env

3. Activate it

    $ source .env/bin/activate

4. Install requirements

    $ pip install -r requirements.txt

5. Synchronize the database:

    $ ./manage.py syncdb
    $ ./manage.py migrate

6. Create a setttings_local.py from template:

    $ cp settings_local.py.dist settings_local.py

7. Open settings_local.py in text editor and changes at least these attributes:

   * DATABASES
   * APP_URL
